data.description: Super Cute 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on a Huge Corner Lot in the Derby School District! Oversized 2 car , Insulated Garage w/ new wifi belt opener ,Newly Renovated/ updated Kitchen with LOTS of storage!  Large master bedroom with oversized Hollywood Bathroom including gorgeous tile floor. Fenced in Back yard with Deck and a New Patio.  Class 4 IR Roof, New and Newer HVAC, Big Beautiful High efficient Large windows throughout installed in 2021!  Wood burning Fireplace in Updated and Finished Family Room. Whole House Attic Fan,  New flooring in basement and new Paint throughout! Zmodo eight ( 8) camera security system with 24/7 recording on local NVR.  New Pretty Blue Front Door with Glass. Storage area on North east side of home. Nearby McConnel Air Force Base.
